1:00:19.599 --> 1:00:20.933
To conclude,

1:00:20.933 --> 1:00:22.935
we bring you greetings

1:00:22.935 --> 1:00:26.205
from Bosnia and Herzegovina.

1:00:26.205 --> 1:00:29.075
This mountainous region has a rich history

1:00:29.075 --> 1:00:31.210
as a traditional meeting place

1:00:31.210 --> 1:00:33.713
between eastern and western cultures;

1:00:33.713 --> 1:00:36.549
it dates from the Middle Ages.

1:00:36.549 --> 1:00:40.186
Because of the diverse religious beliefs 
within the country,

1:00:40.186 --> 1:00:43.423
the 1,160 publishers

1:00:43.423 --> 1:00:46.492
must adapt their preaching methods

1:00:46.492 --> 1:00:49.395
to appeal to the hearts of those who listen.

1:00:49.395 --> 1:00:51.664
This is the city of Mostar,

1:00:51.664 --> 1:00:54.233
which sits on the Neretva River.

1:00:54.233 --> 1:00:55.935
The Neretva River

1:00:55.935 --> 1:00:58.838
flows for nearly 230 kilometers,

1:00:58.838 --> 1:01:00.940
or almost 143 miles.

1:01:02.275 --> 1:01:05.945
Mostar was a former front line 
during the wars of the 1990’s,

1:01:07.113 --> 1:01:09.482
and many buildings still bear the marks

1:01:09.482 --> 1:01:12.919
of the intense fighting that took place.

1:01:12.919 --> 1:01:17.090
Likewise, the aftermath 
left many people in this region

1:01:17.090 --> 1:01:19.892
with emotional and mental scars.

1:01:19.892 --> 1:01:22.829
Our brothers and sisters are working hard

1:01:22.829 --> 1:01:24.897
to bring the hope of something good

1:01:24.897 --> 1:01:28.167
to those in need.

1:01:28.167 --> 1:01:33.072
In the 1930’s, 
a pioneer brother named Alfred Tuček

1:01:33.072 --> 1:01:37.210
spearheaded the preaching work 
in the city of Mostar.

1:01:37.210 --> 1:01:41.881
He was actually one of the first 
in the former Yugoslavia to pioneer.

1:01:41.881 --> 1:01:45.785
Today, the congregation in Mostar 
has about 60 publishers,

1:01:47.019 --> 1:01:51.424
including nine pioneers 
and four field missionaries.

1:01:51.424 --> 1:01:54.427
They bring their warm love and greetings

1:01:54.427 --> 1:01:57.330
to all of us around the world!

1:01:57.330 --> 1:01:59.899
This is JW Broadcasting

1:01:59.899 --> 1:02:10.436
from the world headquarters 
of Jehovah’s Witnesses.
